<bibRefCitation author="LABERGE W" box="[514,670,1528,1550]" pageId="13" pageNumber="18" pagination="191 - 248" refId="ref36004" refString="LABERGE W. E. (1987): A revision of the bees of the genus Andrena of the Western Hemisphere. Part XII. Subgenera Leucandrena, Ptilandrena, Scoliandrena and Melandrena. - Trans. Amer. Ent. Soc. 112: 191 - 248." type="journal article" year="1987">LABERGE 1987</bibRefCitation>
